show.description: Six years after a scandal ruined her life, Shirley returns home with her son to uncover the truth. Working at her sister’s fiancé Neil’s company, unexpected sparks fly — and her son feels an odd bond with him. As secrets unravel, Shirley is determined to find out what really happened that fateful night.
